=A0</em>you get arrested! After is no good.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">It=E2=80=99s not all luck, though. It is plaus=
ible that, now that FTX=E2=80=99s bankruptcy estate is shopping the exchang=
e to buyers, it has a positive value, but when Bankman-Fried was shopping i=
t last year it had a large negative value,=C2=A0<em>because Bankman-Fried w=
as running it then and he=E2=80=99s not now</em>. An exchange that operates=
 pretty well but that is run by a guy who is stealing all the money really =
is worth less, as a going concern, than the shell of that exchange after he=
=E2=80=99s gone.</p>
