<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">A classic crypto trade is:</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Acquire a ton of Bitcoins cheap in li=
ke 2011 and put them in a wallet.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">=
Put the private keys to the wallet onto a password-protected hard drive.</l=
i>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Lose access to the hard drive. The f=
unniest=C2=A0way to do this is by putting the hard drive at the bottom of=
=C2=A0a giant garbage dump, but the easiest way is just to forget the passw=
ord.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Watch the price of Bitcoin go=
 up a lot.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Moan a lot to the media=
 about how you have hundreds of millions of dollars of Bitcoins, but you ca=
n=E2=80=99t get access to them.</li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I am not, like, recommending this trade or any=
thing? I don=E2=80=99t know what you get out of it. Mainly attention? But I=
 <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33142177.286418/a=
HR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMTItMDkvZG9u=
