<ul style=3D"list-style-type: disc; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;">=
=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Minting non-fungible tokens =E2=80=9Co=
f=E2=80=9D his discarded hard drive, and selling them to crypto enthusiasts=
 (sorry, it was 2021), or</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Just sel=
ling heavily discounted shares in his contingent possibility of recovering =
the hard drive (to raise money to try to recover it, or not I suppose).</li=
>
</ul>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Realistically though you are in this trade for=
 attention. You spend a few hundred millions of dollars=E2=80=99 worth of B=
itcoins to be known as the guy who threw away a few hundreds of millions of=
 dollars=E2=80=99 worth of Bitcoins? Why. I suppose another possible trade =
is, just=C2=A0<em>pretend=C2=A0</em>to have the inaccessible hard drive? No=
body=C2=A0<em>else </em>is going to dig up the dump to check.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Well,=C2=A0<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomb=
ergbusiness.com/click/33142177.286418/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud2lyZWQuY29tL3N0b3J5L=
